# Phase cycle routing

When the user asks to run / continue / finish a **phased delivery**, or says
`/phase-cycle`, `Start Stage 1`, `Start Stage 2`, `Start Postman`, `Start E2E`,
`شروع پیاده‌سازی فازها`, or `شروع تست`:

1. Read and follow `~/.cursor/skills/phase-cycle/SKILL.md`
   (or project `.cursor/skills/phase-cycle` if present).
2. Honor the **two-stage** gate: Stage 1 ≠ Stage 2 approval.
3. If no `docs/phase-map.md` (or mapped path), bootstrap from
   `~/.cursor/skills/phase-cycle/BOOTSTRAP.md` and stop for map confirmation.

Do not start real Postman/Playwright/E2E acceptance until Stage 2 is explicitly approved.
